# Input

```yml
failing:
  {
    "object-does-not-fit-within-print-width": "------",
    "TEST": "comma IS added here"
  }

expected:
  {
    "object-fits-within-print-width": "",
    "TEST": "comma NOT here"
  }

---

does not suffice: >
  {
    "object-does-not-fit-within-print-width": "------",
    "TEST": "comma NOT here — but object's now a string due to '>'"
  }

```


